s wonderful view of the water and it is truly a very peaceful place to relax鈭?Poolside service is fast however the food is not the best鈭?Poolside service is just ok, hard to flag a waiter, hard to get more towels, etc鈭?Spa/Gym鈭?Great gym as far as hotels go. Lots of new equipment to work with鈭?Spa is beautiful and treatments are worth the price鈭?Spa exercise classes are a mixed bag. I have taken yoga twice and the first time the instructor was great the second time she was just awful to the point I thought she may injure some new students in the classOver all we love this hotel, however this last time left a few things to be desired. We will return in the future. 
