riendly and professional in accommodating our needs. We accidentally walked in on housekeeping refreshing our room and they were literally on their hands and knees making sure every last detail was perfect. Incredible! And that is what the MO prides it self on. Didn鈥檛 get a chance to even see the spa, sure its top class though.Overall- Great Place, so posh! Definitely the place to be in Miami whether for business or pleasure. 
