<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>The definition of hospitality The Mandarin Oriental-Miami leaves 'no stone unturned' when satisfying their guests. The approach to the hotel and entering the lobby, gives one the immediate 'sense of arrival' that most hotels fail to capture. Having been in the Hotel industry for several years, I take a personal interest in 'critiqueing' each place that I stay. I can honestly say that after staying here for several days, I could not find any noticable flaws worth mentioning. The staff is extremely courteous and professional, the rooms are tastefully done, clean and well-appointed. The small touches throughout our stay gave my wife and I, the feeling that they have truly done it all for us! Without hesitation, I would highly recommend the Manadrin-Miami. They know the true definition of hospitality! What a great job they've done, what a great stay! 
